just sign the contract, finish the degree, buy the house, climb the mountain, we'll finally

11
00:01:00,539 --> 00:01:06,939
be something. Something whole. Something happy. But the truth. The finish line is just another

12
00:01:06,939 --> 00:01:11,200
starting point. And the starting point is always the same.

13
00:01:11,200 --> 00:01:16,299
Our brains are wired for the chase, not the catch. Dopamine doesn't linger. It fades the

14
00:01:16,299 --> 00:01:20,959
